Story*

Once upon a time in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a Jamun 
tree which was on the banks of a river.
In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife.....

The monkey wanted to make a cloth for himself using crocodile skin. He slowly started 
trying to befriend the crocodile bt feeding him the berries. 
The berries were delicious and the crocodile liked it. After sometime the monkey 
started poisoning the berries.....



